# Toast 提示

轻量通知提示（类似 shadcn/sonner）。需要在应用根部挂载一次 `<TxToastHost />`，然后在任意位置调用 `toast()`。

## 基础用法

::TuffDemo{title="Toast" description="挂载 host 后触发提示。" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <template>
    <TxToastHost />
    <TxButton @click="toast({ title: 'Saved', description: 'Your changes have been saved.' })">
      Show toast
    </TxButton>
    <TxButton
      style="margin-left: 8px;"
      @click="toast({ title: 'Success', description: 'Done', variant: 'success' })"
    >
      Success
    </TxButton>
  </template>
---
