## API

### toast(options)

::TuffCodeBlock{lang="ts"}
---
code: |
  toast({
    title?: string
    description?: string
    variant?: 'default' | 'success' | 'warning' | 'danger'
    duration?: number // ms, 0 = 不自动关闭
  })
---
::

### dismissToast / clearToasts

从 `@talex-touch/tuffex/utils` 导入：

::TuffCodeBlock{lang="ts"}
---
code: |
  import { dismissToast, clearToasts } from '@talex-touch/tuffex/utils'
---
::
